                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="8u">

                    <!-- Article list -->
                    <section class="box-article-list">										
                        <!-- Excerpt -->
                        <article class="box-excerpt">
                            <a href="#" class="image image-left">
                                <img src="images/tour/cloud.png" alt="" />
                            </a>
                            <div>
                                <header>
                                    <span class="tour-itemheader">
                                        Free Invoicing with Cloud option
                                    </span>
                                </header>
                                <p>Free invoicing solution lets you get started with ease. We also offer cloud based deployment so you can access from any location where this is availability of internet. No lengthy installations and configurations just a quick setup 
                                and you can get going to manage your business with ease.</p>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        
                        <!-- Excerpt -->
                        <article class="box-excerpt">
                            <a href="#" class="image image-left">
                                <img src="images/tour/workflow.png" alt="" />
                            </a>
                            <div>
                                <header>
                                    <span class="tour-itemheader">
                                        Simple Steamlined Workflow
                                    </span>
                                </header>
                                <p>We offer a simple and easy to follow invoicing workflow. Create clients, products and then invoice them for their purchases.
                                Straight forward and intuitive interface help to achieve this with ease.</p>
                            </div>
                        </article>

                        <!-- Excerpt -->
                        <article class="box-excerpt">
                            <a href="#" class="image image-left">
                                <img src="images/tour/template.png" alt="" />
